particular, the proposed model has\nshown its excellency through comparison with representative theoretical,\nnumerical and experimental data compiled in the contact challenge test by\nMueser et al.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2017 06:34:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-19"}
